headline: Citi upgrades NXP Semiconductors, raises target by $80 on analog recovery
summary: Investing.com -- Citi upgraded NXP Semiconductors NV (NASDAQ:NXPI) to "Buy" from "Neutral" and raised its price target to $290 from $210 citing an imminent recovery in the analog market.
